% Add new BibTeX entries here only after verifying the citation
% against an authoritative source (DOI, journal page, or published
% volume).
%
% Citation key conventions:
%   - Single-author year+keyword (camelCase): e.g.
%     `agresti2013categorical`, `nelsen2006introduction`.
%   - Multi-author or short-form: snake_case `author_year` or
%     `author1_author2_year`: e.g. `fay_herriot_1979`, `wilson_1927`,
%     `agresti_coull_1998`.
%   - Self-citation: `lee_2026_sitemix`.
%
% Keys cited in `dev/02_documentation_audit/02-style-cheatsheet.md`
% and `04-authoring-conventions.md` are authoritative and MUST NOT
% be renamed.
% =====================================================================

